{"article_id":"PMah45dzCeqRpTfP","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Barack Obama ' s bid","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"to assert himself in his final year","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"will begin with long-awaited executive actions on gun control ,","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"expected to be released next week ,","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"shortly after he returns to Washington .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"The White House is putting finishing touches on several measures in an effort","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"to make progress","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"on curbing gun violence , an issue","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"the president and close aides have found frustratingly intractable ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"before the race","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"to replace him","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"enters prime time .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"According to gun industry insiders and others familiar with the proposals ,","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"the changes include requiring an expanded number of small-scale gun sellers to be licensed","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"- and therefore conduct background checks -","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"whenever selling a weapon .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"This wouldn ' t close the so-called gun show loophole ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"though it has the potential","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"to narrow it .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"The administration is also expected to impose tighter rules","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"for reporting guns","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"that get lost or stolen on their way to a buyer .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"Neither comes close to the stronger gun control measures","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"Obama sought in the wake of the 2012 mass shooting of schoolchildren in Sandy Hook","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"and that he has said","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"he still wants .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"But","depth":4},{"id":27,"text":"with Congress unlikely to approve any new gun curbs before the 2016 election ,","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"the measures are in line with what gun-control advocates were hoping","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"would be adopted","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"before Obama leaves office .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"As with every aspect of the president ' s final year , the decisions about the gun actions are being made with a sense of limited time and the 2016 political calendar .","depth":3},{"id":32,"text":"Obama will be returning from his Hawaii vacation ,","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"eager to make a splash ;","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"an earlier-than-normal State of the Union address on Jan. 12 is central to that strategy .","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"But","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"with the Iowa caucuses","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"taking place on Feb. 1 ,","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"Obama will have only a small window","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"to act","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"before the primary melee begins to crowd out other political news .","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"The background check change has been anticipated for months .","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"Obama will tighten the definition","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"of what it means to be \" engaged in the business \" of firearms sales .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"Currently , the law says","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"people","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"who sell guns with the \" principal objective of livelihood and profit \"","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"have to get a dealer ' s license through the Bureau of Alcohol , Tobacco , Firearms and Explosives","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"- and therefore conduct a background check on buyers","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"no matter where they sell ,","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"including online or at a gun show .","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"It ' s unclear whether a lot more dealers would line up for licenses .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"But gun-control advocates say","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"a better definition would make it much easier to prosecute sellers","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"who should ,","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"but don ' t .","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"Only about half of the people","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"who are tried","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"for selling guns","depth":14},{"id":59,"text":"without a license","depth":14},{"id":60,"text":"are convicted by juries ,","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"according to a report from Everytown , the pro-gun control group","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"led by former New York Mayor Michael Bloomberg .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"In an interview , Everytown officials couldn ' t confirm","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"whether the White House was heeding their advice .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"But ,","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"said legal director Liz Avore ,","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"\" Any kind of clarification would be beneficial in this context","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"because right now most sellers and prosecutors are kind of flying blind . \"","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"It 's not clear whether Obama has settled on final language yet .","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"But as one of the major proponents of a change , Everytown has recommended adding several factors to the definition","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"- including selling guns in their original packaging ,","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"reselling a gun shortly after acquiring it ,","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"maintaining a certain quantity of guns for sale or selling more than 25 guns a year -","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"as possible signals","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"that someone needs a license .","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"A top gun industry executive defended the current definition ,","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"it requires dealers to make most of their living from gun sales","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"before requiring a license .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"Based on conversations with ATF officials this month ,","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"the executive described the upcoming change as `` overreach '' :","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"\" If you are not doing it for the principal purpose","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"of earning a livelihood","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"AND earn a profit ,","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"you are not engaged in the business","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"as defined by Congress , \"","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"he said in an email .","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"Another victory for advocates is likely to be a requirement for all licensed dealers and manufacturers to report to federal authorities any guns","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"that are stolen in transit to a buyer","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"as missing from their inventory .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"Currently ,","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"advocates say ,","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"thieves often target packages","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"addressed to gun retailers","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"in the hopes","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"of stealing unregistered guns","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"that are harder to trace .","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"And","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"while buyer and seller might sort out refunds or replacements on their own ,","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"they ' re not required to report the missing guns to the National Crime Information Center .","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"ATF first proposed the new regulation in August 2014 ,","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"which industry opposed ,","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"a voluntary reporting program was working just fine .","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"But the year-and-a-half lag between the rule ' s proposal and finalization is another factor","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"urging Obama to act forcefully","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"as he enters the last year in his term .","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"It is not clear whether the measure will take the form of a new regulation","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"( which would take months longer to finish","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"because of requirements for public comment )","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"or clarification of an existing rule ,","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"which would take less time","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"but might not carry as much weight with the courts -","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"or a future administration .","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"\" We have not been told that they are drafting a proposed rule , \"","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"the industry executive said .","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"\" But it remains to be seen . \"","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"The White House declined to comment on the substance of the executive actions or their timing .","depth":5},{"id":119,"text":"Communications Director Jen Psaki told reporters at an event","depth":7},{"id":120,"text":"hosted by Bloomberg News in mid-December","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"that the new gun measures were coming in \" weeks , not months . \"","depth":6},{"id":122,"text":"This latest round of executive moves follows 23 actions","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"related to gun violence","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"that Obama ordered in 2013 , in the months","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"following the Sandy Hook massacre ,","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"plus two more in 2014 .","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"During that same period , Vice President Joe Biden led a failed campaign with congressional Democrats","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"to pass a bill","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"to impose near-universal background checks .","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"The president ' s announcement of new gun actions will be more like his immigration executive orders in late 2014","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"- currently held up by the courts -","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"issued as part of a broader campaign","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"to pressure Congress","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"and draw a contrast with Republicans .","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"White House senior adviser Valerie Jarrett also raised gun-control advocates ' hopes for new domestic violence provisions last month .","depth":7},{"id":136,"text":"In a post on the actress Lena Dunham ' s website , Jarrett noted","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"that guns are the most likely cause of death for women","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"who are victims of domestic partner violence .","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"Gun-control activists acknowledged","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"that changing the rules for licenses might have limited impact on what sellers actually do in the short term .","depth":8},{"id":141,"text":"But in this political environment , they ' ll take whatever measures they can ,","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"no matter how incremental .","depth":8},{"id":143,"text":"\" Setting cultural norms , ''","depth":8},{"id":144,"text":"said Everytown research director Ted Alcorn ,","depth":8},{"id":145,"text":"`` is something","depth":8},{"id":146,"text":"that laws do . ''","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":293,"left":177,"right":292,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":177,"left":151,"right":176,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":148,"right":150,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":148,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":2,"right":149,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":176,"left":171,"right":175,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":171,"left":157,"right":170,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":154,"right":156,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":5,"right":153,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":6,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":7,"right":